Class PhotoGallery

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301.t03.photo.PhotoGallery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable, Observer, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class PhotoGallery
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable, Observer, java.lang.Cloneable
    class PhotoGallery encapsulates a collection of Photos

    This model is used often in the application in such place as EditItemView, AddItemView, InspectItemView, as well as the inventory browse fragments.
